yingyinNormal.en: We have to see Professor Dumbledore. Immediately!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们要见邓布利多教授，这会儿就得见。

yingyinNormal.en: You are to cease all activities here immediately.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你要立刻终止这里的所有研究。

yingyinNormal.en: Immediately, sir! No interlopers!
yingyinNormal.zh: 马上带走，先生！闲人勿扰！
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《爱丽丝梦游仙境2：镜中奇遇记》

yingyinNormal.en: Lidewij, play Bomfalleralla immediately.
yingyinNormal.zh: 莉德蔼，放一下彭法罗拉这首歌。

yingyinNormal.en: Would you like the job? Yes! Can you start immediately? Yes!
yingyinNormal.zh: 你想要这份工作吗？想。你能马上就开始上班吗？能。

yingyinNormal.en: A nearby cell sees the warning and immediately goes into action.
yingyinNormal.zh: 旁边一个细胞看到了这个警示，立刻开始行动。

yingyinNormal.en: Madam, please, put on a lifebelt. Get to the boat deck immediately.
yingyinNormal.zh: 女士，请穿救生衣到救生艇甲板。

yingyinNormal.en: Because that would set off the bomb immediately and we'll all be dead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 按下它炸弹会立刻爆炸，然后我们就都死定了。

yingyinNormal.en: I concur. Tiger girl, we need to leave immediately. I don't even know you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我赞同，虎妞，咱们得赶快走。我都不认识你。

yingyinNormal.en: If you watch the children, you will immediately notice how honest they are.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看看小孩，你马上就能看到他们有多诚实。
